### Foto de perfil
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/perfil/foto/
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MiBoundary

--MiBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="imagen"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./avatar.jpg
--MiBoundary--